      <div class="br-label">kbps</div>
      <div class="br-desc">Good balance of size and quality for most music</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="purple-box">
    <p><strong>Converting from FLAC?</strong> Always use 320kbps. Since FLAC is lossless, you want to preserve as much of that quality as possible in the MP3. Going lower only loses more detail unnecessarily.</p>
  </div>

